    public class StandardBullhornData

    Standard implementation of the BullhornData interface that manages all rest calls and data binding from/to json - java.

    This class can be injected using the standard @Autowired syntax:

    Author:
    Magnus Fiore Palm
    See Also:
    for session management, for http calls, for how to pass in parameters to the specific methods, for json/java conversion, for assembling the urls for the api calls, for adding the specific variables needed for the api calls, for file management related to resume parsing and file api calls, for error handling
